<p><i>How ETS works</i></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.defra.gov.uk/ENVIRONMENT/climatechange/trading/eu/" class="external text" title="http://www.defra.gov.uk/ENVIRONMENT/climatechange/trading/eu/" rel="nofollow">UK Defra General overview at the UK Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.pewclimate.org/docUploads/EU-ETS%20White%20Paper.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.pewclimate.org/docUploads/EU-ETS%20White%20Paper.pdf" rel="nofollow">Pew Center White Paper&#160;: overview of EU ETS</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.inagendo.com/res/doc/inagendo_ets_fact_book.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.inagendo.com/res/doc/inagendo_ets_fact_book.pdf" rel="nofollow">Emission Trading Fact Book of Inagendo (contains, among others, a glossary of ETS terms</a></li>
</ul>
<p><i>Key reports, and assessments</i></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://reports.eea.europa.eu/technical_report_2008_3/en" class="external text" title="http://reports.eea.europa.eu/technical_report_2008_3/en" rel="nofollow">Application of the Emissions Trading Directive by EU Member States - reporting year 2007</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.isi.fhg.de/n/Projekte/pdf/NAP2_assessment.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.isi.fhg.de/n/Projekte/pdf/NAP2_assessment.pdf" rel="nofollow">Fraunhofer Institute November 2006 assessment of preliminary Phase 2 NAPs</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.ecofys.com/com/publications/gate.asp?fn=documents/Ecofys_Summary_InitialNAP2_Assessment.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.ecofys.com/com/publications/gate.asp?fn=documents/Ecofys_Summary_InitialNAP2_Assessment.pdf" rel="nofollow">Ecofys evaluation of preliminary Phase 2 NAPs</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.ecofys.co.uk/uk/publications/documents/Interim_Report_NAP_Evaluation_180804.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.ecofys.co.uk/uk/publications/documents/Interim_Report_NAP_Evaluation_180804.pdf" rel="nofollow">Ecofys evaluation of Phase 1 NAPs</a>. ECOFYS, August 2004.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.climnet.org/EUenergy/ET/NAPsReport_Summary0306.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.climnet.org/EUenergy/ET/NAPsReport_Summary0306.pdf" rel="nofollow">National Allocation Plans 2005-7: Do they deliver?</a> Executive summary of report by Climate Action Network.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.climnet.org/EUenergy/ET/20050515%20CO2%20emissions%20joint%20PR%20_final.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.climnet.org/EUenergy/ET/20050515%20CO2%20emissions%20joint%20PR%20_final.pdf" rel="nofollow">Climate Action Network Europe</a> "CO2 emissions: EU member states abuse Emissions Trading System" Press release, 15 May 2006</li>
<li><a href="http://www.carbontradewatch.org" class="external text" title="http://www.carbontradewatch.org" rel="nofollow">Carbon Trade Watch</a></li>
<li><a href="http://reports.eea.europa.eu/technical_report_2008_6/en" class="external text" title="http://reports.eea.europa.eu/technical_report_2008_6/en" rel="nofollow">Annual European Community greenhouse gas inventory 1990 - 2006 and inventory report 2008</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.panda.org/about_wwf/where_we_work/europe/what_we_do/epo/initiatives/climate/publications/index.cfm?uNewsID=50500" class="external text" title="http://www.panda.org/about_wwf/where_we_work/europe/what_we_do/epo/initiatives/climate/publications/index.cfm?uNewsID=50500" rel="nofollow">WWF website</a> "The environmental effectiveness and economic efficiency of the EU ETS: Structural aspects of the allocation". by WWF and Öko-Institut, 09 Nov 2005.</li>
</ul>


